Recipe Name: 1. Cut Chicken into small pieces then mix with Cajun, Paprika, Chicken Spice, Salt, Pepper, and 1 Cal Spray.
2. Fry mixture in pan for 10 minutes or until golden and cooked through.
3. Remove chicken and shred with 2 forks.
4. Cut Rashers into 1cm2 pieces, scissors are easiest. Then fry in pan until cooked and brown.
5. Mix Chicken, Rashers, Lettuce, and mayocue together in a bowl.
